{
  "stem": "11184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they came in after it was over, this selection was over, and we were together again-- the four of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got sick-- typhoid, diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister and me, we both got very ill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we slept.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had-- I had 'dysenteria'-- 'dysen-terry'-- dysentery?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And hers turned out to be typhoid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hundreds and thousands of young people were putting piles of bodies. 'Cause I went into the mortuary, and I saw piles and piles of bodies-- oh, in the thousands.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just-- mine-- we drank from the same glass, you know-- both of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so this is when I lost my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, but just-- just threw them in, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- no, no, no, no, no-- separate-- separate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But just threw them in on a board.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no other things to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and then my father, we didn't tell my father that she passed away for a while, because he was ill.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time he got ill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he-- he suffered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In-- in 1943, in July, he passed away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had, what do you call?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "TB-- TB-- and they couldn't-- nothing could be done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The doctor told us-- the Jewish-- a ghetto doctor-- if the war ends, he has a chance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if it doesn't, so-- he can't make it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with no-- they couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was also in a so-called hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they send him home, and he choked to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was summer-- one little room, no air-- absolutely no air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a horrible, horrible thing to watch-- horrible for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
